Full Description: ExoVentures quickly realized that honest, dedicated, driven, and talented people are hard to come by! Funds are also scarce, even when they asked expert consultants for help, they often refused to be bound by performance-driven profit-sharing. Although they agree that everyone must be paid what they are worth, how could they distinguish a dud from a winning mentor? In their early-stage condition, the only logical way was by tying compensation to results, which guaranteed that everyone had skin in the game! The results: Only talented, driven souls applied, and they exploded within 3 years to a $6.8 Million dollar company! That's when they decided to turn in the reins serving a single firm, to launch exoVentures, LLC and lead many, albeit vetted, early-stage companies to equal or better results.
